Timsort是一种执行速度快、并且可以在任何时候间隔内进行快速排序的算法。在Python中，Timsort算法由Jeffrey Dean于2002年发明。该算法使用多个窗口来排序一组数据。每个窗口对应一段范围，它的长度为最大窗口大小（可选值：4，8，16）。

在Lean 4中，我们可以在 `libraries.std.stdlib` 包中找到Timsort函数：
```rust
// @include timsort.rs
// rust-lang/rust#17603
fn timsort_ref(xs: &mut [T], cmp: impl FnMut(&T, &T) -> Ordering) {
    // This function is `O(n log n)` for an array with n elements, where `n` is the length of the array.
    // It is also `O(n)` for a sorted array with a constant-time comparison function, and thus can be used
    // as a stable sort that also sorts in place.  See https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timsort#Performance for more details.
    let mut pivot = xs[0];
    let mut tpivot = 0;
    let mut tl = tpivot;
    let mut tr = xs.len() - 1;
    while tl < tr {
        if cmp(&pivot, &xs[tl]) < Ordering::Equal {
            tl += 1;
        } else if cmp(&pivot, &xs[tr]) > Ordering::Equal {
            tr -= 1;
        } else { // cmp(&pivot, &xs[tl]) == Ordering::Equal && cmp(&pivot, &xs[tr]) == Ordering::Equal => pivot = xs[tl]; return;
            pivot = xs[tl]; tl += 1; tr -= 1; tpivot = tl; continue; } } } }
```

